description: I enjoy gardening, fishing, camping, hiking and going for walks. I also like preparing dinners for special occasions. I studied Economics and Finance in University and later returned to get an Engineering degree. I'm looking for a woman that is family orientated, fun to be with, flexible, honest, trustworthy and loyal. I'm not here to play games but to hopefully find the right woman for me.
name: Edis43t

description:
5' 2'' and young at heart. I enjoy the beach and dancing, both rock n roll and ballroom. Well travelled, loyal, gentle, sensitive & caring with a cheeky/dry sense of humour. Normally reserved in manner although occasionally the 'wild child' escapes. Dislike cold weather, an avid reader, can often be found sitting in the sun with a good book. 

My cup is neither half full or half empty... I fill it up! 

Other interests: boating, kayaking, computers, bbq with friends, dabbling on the stock market & researching the property market. Reasonably adventurous although no amount of bribery will tempt me to try bungee jumping. 

My ideal partner would be a clean shaven non smoker and have a compatible chemistry. Someone capable in thought and deed, willing to dress up occasionally, prefer comfort to roughing it and enjoy sun, swimming, boating, dancing & cuddles. Someone to share the finer things as well as simple pleasures like rainbows and sunsets. A man prepared to give friendship a try and see what develops. Is this you...?
name: spectrumAU
